  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>For the Peace and Order of the Universe!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rocket Squad is a team-based first-person shooter.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Infiltrate perilous planets, gather resources, and return safely to your shelter.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Utilize each character's unique abilities and strategically form your team to restore order to the universe.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3315230/extras/48aa25c70a18dd879b916ad7845dd6c7.avif?t=1748590039\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3315230/extras_big/48aa25c70a18dd879b916ad7845dd6c7.avif?t=1748590039 width=800 height=326 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Agents</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each character possesses unique abilities.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Analyze their strengths and assemble your team strategically.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3315230/extras/4f8069b44c33a14cce5b39fe739f13a3.poster.avif?t=1748590039\" width=616 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3315230/extras/4f8069b44c33a14cce5b39fe739f13a3.webm?t=1748590039\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3315230/extras/4f8069b44c33a14cce5b39fe739f13a3.mp4?t=1748590039\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Budget Management</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every action consumes funds, and lack of resources can severely hinder mission performance.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Manage your finances carefully before and after each operation, and use your team’s budget without waste.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Efficient financial management is the key to victory.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3315230/extras/67a7c89723b314d5e98810416db58344.poster.avif?t=1748590039\" width=616 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3315230/extras/67a7c89723b314d5e98810416db58344.webm?t=1748590039\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3315230/extras/67a7c89723b314d5e98810416db58344.mp4?t=1748590039\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Planet Infiltration</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The economic order of the universe has collapsed.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The development of the Infinity Quantum Core has enabled infinite cryptocurrency mining, causing this catastrophe.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Infiltrate dangerous planets to restore peace and order to the universe.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3315230/extras/17ef4e610cf0a5aea34130a66cc0d98d.poster.avif?t=1748590039\" width=616 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3315230/extras/17ef4e610cf0a5aea34130a66cc0d98d.webm?t=1748590039\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3315230/extras/17ef4e610cf0a5aea34130a66cc0d98d.mp4?t=1748590039\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Combat Against Robots</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The robots have monopolized the Infinity Quantum Core, bringing ruin to the universe's economy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >They are no longer mere machines.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Face off against the wealthy robots who have become enemies of the universe.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3315230/extras/2d1ff238658e55ccf15eb348bba20582.poster.avif?t=1748590039\" width=616 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3315230/extras/2d1ff238658e55ccf15eb348bba20582.webm?t=1748590039\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3315230/extras/2d1ff238658e55ccf15eb348bba20582.mp4?t=1748590039\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Economic Recovery</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Obtain valuable items and escape safely.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Raid the vaults of the affluent robots and secure the future of a struggling universe.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3315230/extras/ad4d3c21bbeb0815cc9a97e47d443d84.poster.avif?t=1748590039\" width=616 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3315230/extras/ad4d3c21bbeb0815cc9a97e47d443d84.webm?t=1748590039\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3315230/extras/ad4d3c21bbeb0815cc9a97e47d443d84.mp4?t=1748590039\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Player Enhancement</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enhance your character’s abilities with a variety of artifacts.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Combine artifacts that suit your character’s traits to develop your own unique playstyle.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3315230/extras/b20ca1608dc9bc110f813a0e7be4164d.poster.avif?t=1748590039\" width=616 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3315230/extras/b20ca1608dc9bc110f813a0e7be4164d.webm?t=1748590039\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3315230/extras/b20ca1608dc9bc110f813a0e7be4164d.mp4?t=1748590039\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Shelter Customization</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your shelter is your safe haven.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Decorate it with various furniture and ornaments to make it truly yours.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3315230/extras/eb39b3fba2a7e99b389d896b6bb455fe.poster.avif?t=1748590039\" width=616 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3315230/extras/eb39b3fba2a7e99b389d896b6bb455fe.webm?t=1748590039\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3315230/extras/eb39b3fba2a7e99b389d896b6bb455fe.mp4?t=1748590039\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Multiplayer</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Form a squad with up to four friends and save the universe together!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3315230/extras/1e6d0d95069374c8ce807a5529ea75aa.poster.avif?t=1748590039\" width=616 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3315230/extras/1e6d0d95069374c8ce807a5529ea75aa.webm?t=1748590039\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3315230/extras/1e6d0d95069374c8ce807a5529ea75aa.mp4?t=1748590039\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
